Monorepo managed with [Moon](https://moonrepo.dev) and [Proto](https://moonrepo.dev/proto).

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install runtimes via proto
proto install

# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Run all tasks
moon run :build
```

## Structure

- `{{structure.apps}}/` — Applications
- `{{structure.packages}}/` — Shared packages and configs
- `{{structure.modules}}/` — Modules

## Adding tools

```bash
# Set up a tool workspace-wide (e.g. prettier, eslint, tsconfig)
aikuora add prettier

# Scaffold a new app
aikuora add nextjs --name my-app

# Link a tool config to an existing project
aikuora add prettier apps/my-app

# Fork a built-in tool to customize it locally
aikuora add prettier --local
```
